{"tid":1588152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚神獸不完美，可改善","createTime":"2019-09-22T16:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T16:47:34.000Z","uid":35592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"62adff5256f61fc9957402fde2beafa7851adf49","tid":1588152,"uid":35592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:36:58.000Z","msg":"大家召喚神獸個陣要記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">制暴</span></span>兩個字<br />\n係自衛還擊，唔係主動攻擊唔同政見既人<br />\n個D 攞住玻璃樽攞住刀個D 緊係要出手<br />\n但係街9 UP，撕文宣就忍一忍<br />\n要顧一顧形象，因為道德係我地既力量，亦係我地支持者既來源<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雖然我唔同意你既論點，但我會捍衛你說話既權利</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我都明白大家既憤怒，但係我地唔可以因為憤怒而放棄我地既信念、我地既價值<br />\n和勇不割，只希望可以改善<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qkd1cSs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQkd1cSs.png&h=ea7d64c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b535495a2eda0d17ab5fd5311b4b4796454baa76","tid":1588152,"uid":35592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:37:14.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"3678f5abc9ed633d4b32bd15c32954c7b7e615f8","tid":1588152,"uid":35592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:37:24.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"c856a98364d56a01d2a5b069a5c434c00c7d2a15","tid":1588152,"uid":35592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:37:40.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"00c62d1dc757b1ee0beba4fc5dea6ef6b8b135ee","tid":1588152,"uid":35592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:37:53.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"0f049c1021523d86026bcb3d4b67c2fd7a097297","tid":1588152,"uid":35592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:38:09.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"44e37c04b07c823c07d89c82891210ef0e53a973","tid":1588152,"uid":35592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:38:30.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"40eb53c6e2814fa07ae16719f8d5e677afb32061","tid":158